dev-1.x.name: drupal/depositphotos

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

dev-1.x.description: This module gives you the opportunity to use and publish illustrations with affiliate links from Depositphotos, one of the leading photobanks in the world. After adding the keywords, Depositphotos will suggest relevant and themed images. You will be able to get relevant visual content and profit from your readers.
